07/20/2017:


Bassett Announces New Division to Expand Club Level Product Line

BASSETT, Va., July 19, 2017 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Bassett Furniture Industries, Inc. (NASDAQ:BSET), a leading manufacturer and marketer of home furnishings, today announced the formation of a new division to expand its motion product line. The Club Level Motion Division will be led by Bruce Cohenour, senior vice president of sales and merchandising, and will focus on expanding the motion product line nationally with its independent retailers.
“Bassett continues to seek new avenues to pursue sales growth as we look to the future. .....

