Somewhat Positive Media Coverage Somewhat Unlikely to Affect Bassett Furniture Industries, (BSET) Stock Price

News stories about Bassett Furniture Industries, (NASDAQ:BSET) have trended somewhat positive this week, according to Accern. The research firm scores the sentiment of media coverage by analyzing more than 20 million blog and news sources in real time. Accern ranks coverage of public companies on a scale of negative one to positive one, with scores closest to one being the most favorable. Bassett Furniture Industries, earned a daily sentiment score of 0.23 on Accern’s scale. .....

